race.comment: DARKBONEE (1) returned in good order with a near-miss at Warrnambool. Followed by a comfortable win at Sandown-Lakeside over a mile this grade. Carries 3kg more, but he's an improving galloper who's still very well-placed. VELLASMACHINE (2) turned in a nice effort to score two runs ago at this track. Came back 16-days later and didn't have much luck over this distance. Has a key jockey switch to the in-form Kersley and can go a lot better. JUMPINMYCAR (8) is heading in the right direction. Needs to find a bit more, but that's not out of the question. JACKAND (4) showed enough here last time over the trip to include on an each-way basis.
